{"tid":2359011,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國研究：武漢稱無臨床確診病例後 仍有數以萬計人染疫無病徵 或令疫情死灰復燃","createTime":"2021-01-08T14:11:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T14:38:27.000Z","uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e3193accd208438c5618243bd95153c58a6bdf52","tid":2359011,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T14:11:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6-%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E7%A8%B1%E7%84%A1%E8%87%A8%E5%BA%8A%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E7%97%85%E4%BE%8B%E5%BE%8C-%E4%BB%8D%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%A5%E8%90%AC%E8%BF%91%E4%BA%BA%E6%9F%93%E7%96%AB%E7%84%A1%E7%97%85%E5%BE%B5-%E6%88%96%E4%BB%A4%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E6%AD%BB%E7%81%B0%E5%BE%A9%E7%87%83/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2F%25E5%2581%25A5%25E5%25BA%25B7%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6-%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%2587%25A8%25E5%25BA%258A%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E7%2597%2585%25E4%25BE%258B%25E5%25BE%258C-%25E4%25BB%258D%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E8%2590%25AC%25E8%25BF%2591%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%259F%2593%25E7%2596%25AB%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%2597%2585%25E5%25BE%25B5-%25E6%2588%2596%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E7%2581%25B0%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E7%2587%2583%2F&d=M%2BQ4vsyFJ%2Bls%2BsYkNkBEXUBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=bcdb6ebd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2F%25E5%2581%25A5%25E5%25BA%25B7%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6-%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%2587%25A8%25E5%25BA%258A%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E7%2597%2585%25E4%25BE%258B%25E5%25BE%258C-%25E4%25BB%258D%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E8%2590%25AC%25E8%25BF%2591%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%259F%2593%25E7%2596%25AB%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%2597%2585%25E5%25BE%25B5-%25E6%2588%2596%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E7%2581%25B0%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E7%2587%2583%2F&h=c78a17b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6-%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E7%A8%B1%E7%84%A1%E8%87%A8%E5%BA%8A%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E7%97%85%E4%BE%8B%E5%BE%8C-%E4%BB%8D%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%A5%E8%90%AC%E8%BF%91%E4%BA%BA%E6%9F%93%E7%96%AB%E7%84%A1%E7%97%85%E5%BE%B5-%E6%88%96%E4%BB%A4%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E6%AD%BB%E7%81%B0%E5%BE%A9%E7%87%83/</a><br />\n<br />\n最新刊於《PLOS 被忽視熱帶疾病》的中國研究對超過 6 萬名健康人士進行病毒抗體測試，發現有逾 1,100 萬人口的武漢，即使聲稱市內的武漢肺炎（COVID-19）疫情受控後，仍有以萬計居民感染了 COVID-19 而無病徵繼續傳播病毒，令疫情在中國死灰復燃。<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯在新研究中，武漢大學團隊分析了 2020 年 3 月 6 日至 5 月 3 日，共 63,107 人身上採集的血液樣本中 IgG 和 IgM 抗體的出現率。所有接受測試的人都是健康的，並曾接受篩查然後才可復工。<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯研究人員估計， 2020 年 3 月至 5 月間，武漢市有數以萬計人曾感染而無病徵，期間該市無發現臨床確診 COVID-19 病例，但團隊在報告中未有明言實際數字。<br />\n<br />\n武漢市的 IgM 陽性率亦分別⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n團隊結論是，在消除武漢市 COVID-19 的臨床確診病例後，存在大量無症狀 SARS-CoV-2 攜帶者，而無毒的 SARS-CoV-2 病毒株可能仍會在極易感人群中引起症狀，這些病毒株也可能重新演變成高毒性病毒株，令中國疫情死灰復燃。<br />\n<br />\n雖然官方近期加強 COVID-19 非源自中國的論述，但武漢市仍然是全球第一個公佈出現 COVID-19 的地方，而且由 2019 年 12 月至去年 5 月，全球感染病例有近三分之二都來自中國。<br />\n<br />\n來源：<br />\nMedicalXpress, COVID-19 likely lingered longer than reported in Wuhan: study, 7 January 2021<br />\n<br />\n報告：<br />\nDuan, S.H., Zhou, M.Y., Zhang, W. &amp; et al. (2021). Seroprevalence and asymptomatic carrier status of SARS-CoV-2 in Wuhan City and other places of China. PLOS Neglected Tropical Diseases 15(1): e0008975. doi: 10.1371/journal.pntd.0008975<br />\n<br />\n文／Alan Chiu"},{"pid":"beb67bad2da08c624d8692d2db5a55832914a9a1","tid":2359011,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T14:22:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P32QxtF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP32QxtF.png&h=539ac01a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wc0bgVf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwc0bgVf.png&h=2cde84e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/437ti85.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F437ti85.png&h=7b96181b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a883120e6984530cca45f4d907533f4517bd51cc","tid":2359011,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T14:38:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YZg2VAF.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYZg2VAF.gif&h=38390d61&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}